Package fr.sorbonne_u.sylalexcenter.performancecontroller.interfaces

Interface PerformanceControllerServicesHandlerI

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdmissionController
    public interface PerformanceControllerServicesHandlerI
    The interface PerformanceControllerServicesHandlerI defines the methods used by the performance controller component in order to communicate with the admission controller when an AVM is added or removed, or when cores are added or removed.
    Author:
    Alexandra Tudor, Sylia Righi
